  "where_it_fits": "Accessed from the Activity Chooser while in a course (typically via Course Edit Mode) and used during course authoring; upon save it creates the assignment and returns to or opens the assignment page within the Course Page where it appears in the Course Index and activity breadcrumbs. It is part of the course content creation flow reachable from the course interface (Course tab, Course Index sidebar, and edit controls).",
